                    <span>Written from the heart, and it shows.  Truly a magnificent piece of work from Henry Thomas.  I loved this book from beginning to end.  Follow Walter Johnson from beginning to end through the eyes of someone that actually cares about Walter Johnson, his grandson.  I cannot say enough great things about this book.  Such a teriffic treat about a wonderful character in the history of baseball.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">too much game description</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
